<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS FOR OUR COUNTRY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I gam lungsietum ka Lalpa Isu hung leng hen,
 Malai Galili gam a A len bang khan;
 Zingdawng Sawl No Lalpa Isu,
 Hung suok henla namtin suihlung,
 Ni bangin vaksak hen,
 Zan thim nuoia umte A vakah,
 Nga bangin leng hitiu.

[V2]
 I gam lungsiet um ah,
 Lal Isu lili pakin lun leh;
 Suihlungah kipahna leh,
 Muonna chuh nei hiting;
 Sietlei gamdang cheng sang I gam chuh,
 Gam vangnei hung hina.

[V3]
 2. Thiemna, chitna, thaihkawi in I gam hihhawih puona,
 Lal Isu nga banga A lenloh ngal chun;
 Sietlei thiemna, chitna haw hin,
 Kipahna kim leh lautha muonna;
 Ei pie thei puona,
 I gam suhawih dingin Lal Isu,
 Nga bangin hungleng hen.

[V4]
 3. I gam muoltin ah lawnlei heisa pakin a lun,
 Lengnga buolna dingin damtui thieng a luong;
 I gam hawihna leh nunnawp na'n,
 Kipahna kim leh nunnawp na kim;
 Ei pie thei puona,
 Nunnawp kimna dingin Lal Isu,
 Nga bangin hungleng hen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>190</hymn_number>
</song>